cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on learning manipulation tasks for robots. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper uses multiple RGB cameras to learn the tasks without building an explicit 3D representation. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses an end-to-end learning approach to accomplish the tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper uses a multi-view approach to learn precise manipulation tasks. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with controlling robotic agents to perform manipulation tasks.
